cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SI, cs.SE, cs.DC

The paper discusses the spread of mobile phone viruses and corresponding countermeasures, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper specifically focuses on the spread of viruses through multimedia message services (MMS), which involves network infrastructure (cs.NI) and social networks (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the effectiveness of controlling methods, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
